dde-file-manager-vcs-plugin (0.5.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Major feature release with 74+ commits since v0.1.0
  * feat: Complete UI overhaul with GitKraken-style interface design
  * feat: Add comprehensive Git Remote Manager functionality
  * feat: Implement advanced push and pull dialogs with impact assessment
  * feat: Add commit file diff dialog with syntax highlighting support
  * feat: Enhance GitLogDialog with remote commit tracking and branch management
  * feat: Add "Open in Browser" functionality for commits
  * feat: Implement asynchronous remote connection testing
  * feat: Add file preview functionality with special renderer support
  * feat: Enhance GitCommitDialog with improved file management and context menus
  * feat: Add loading status indicators and progress feedback
  * feat: Implement column width management and UI layout optimizations
  * feat: Add syntax highlighting support for CMake and QML files
  * feat: Enhance GitCheckoutDialog with branch comparison features
  * feat: Add context menu functionality for commit actions
  * feat: Implement progressive search functionality in Git dialogs
  * refactor: Centralize dialog management in GitDialogManager
  * refactor: Optimize command cancellation and process handling
  * refactor: Improve success and failure handling across all dialogs
  * refactor: Clean up UI layouts and improve button styling
  * fix: Enhance Git dialog initialization and error handling
  * fix: Prevent recursive updates and improve stability
  * chore: Update Qt version compatibility in CMakeLists

